00:01:07.500 --> 00:01:12.960
So we feel-- with a little
bit of misgivings, today, I'm

00:01:12.960 --> 00:01:17.610
going to be emceeing and walking
through a lot of projects that

00:01:17.610 --> 00:01:22.620
don't represent my
thinking or my work at all,

00:01:22.620 --> 00:01:25.980
and instead represent the
fine ideas of these people,

00:01:25.980 --> 00:01:28.110
and hope that I
can get most of it

00:01:28.110 --> 00:01:30.000
right-- that we can
get a kind of overview.

00:01:30.000 --> 00:01:32.625
And then we're going to pull out
a couple of different projects

00:01:32.625 --> 00:01:36.960
