How do we pull the
picture together

00:02:53.910 --> 00:02:55.950
with all of these
different kinds of projects

00:02:55.950 --> 00:02:58.980
and understand from a
broader perspective where

00:02:58.980 --> 00:03:02.250
the university ought
to be around making

00:03:02.250 --> 00:03:05.440
the curriculum
visible for students,

00:03:05.440 --> 00:03:10.110
for faculty, and
