And so early on
when we were talking

00:11:11.180 --> 00:11:14.000
about these curricular
mapping ideas,

00:11:14.000 --> 00:11:16.800
and he met Karen
Willcox, and he was like,

00:11:16.800 --> 00:11:19.325
I can do this in
the gov department.

00:11:19.325 --> 00:11:20.600
I can build something.

