And it seemed like the
next week there was

00:11:22.640 --> 00:11:23.990
something for us to look at.

00:11:23.990 --> 00:11:25.040
And he began to iterate.

00:11:25.040 --> 00:11:27.669
And of course, that
early view moved

00:11:27.669 --> 00:11:29.210
into a number of
different directions

00:11:29.210 --> 00:11:32.540
that he's going to talk about.

