where we're expanding

00:12:15.530 --> 00:12:18.230
and doing something
that's more systematic.

00:12:18.230 --> 00:12:21.920
And what we've tried
to do is put in red

00:12:21.920 --> 00:12:25.802
where we think these
projects are now.

