00:36:14.330 --> 00:36:16.400
conceptual question in
quantum mechanics about

00:36:16.400 --> 00:36:18.530
the eigenfunction of a
Schroedinger equation

00:36:18.530 --> 00:36:21.060
for a semi infinite's--
well, anyway, I won't go on.

00:36:21.060 --> 00:36:23.300
[LAUGHING]

